
config SPRD_CAM_PW_DOMAIN_R4P0
	bool "Spreadtrum Camera Power Domain R4P0 for Pike2"
	depends on SPRD_CAMERA
	help
            This is a power domain driver for Spreadtrum SOCs
            and pike2. This driver open and close some clocks for pike2 Cam Sys.
            If you want to use this config,
            please read spec and driver code, they can help you to use r4p0 driver

config SPRD_CAM_PW_DOMAIN_R5P0
	bool "Spreadtrum Camera Power Domain R5P0"
	depends on SPRD_CAMERA
	help
	    This is a power domain driver for cam & dispc sys.

